  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Ion Battery from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cobalt</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ferrite dust</span>. Use <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> to craft in empty <span class=\"name name-technology\">Inventory Slots</span>.<br>Cobalt is found underground. Locate natural cave entrances. <span class=\"name name-red\">WARNING:</span> many caves contain hazardous flora.<br>Supplies are occasionally found in <span class=\"name name-technology\">Supply Caches</span> left on planets.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">铁氧体粉末</span>制作离子电池。使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> 在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">库存栏位</span>中制作。<br>钴能在地下被找到。寻找天然洞穴的入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>许多洞穴中存在危险植物群系。<br>补给品偶尔能从留在行星上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">物资贮存箱</span>中找到。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">铁氧体粉末</span>制作离子电池。使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> 在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">库存栏位</span>中制作。<br>钴能在地下被找到。寻找天然洞穴的入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>许多洞穴中存在危险植物群系。<br>补给品偶尔能从留在行星上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">物资贮存箱</span>中找到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">鈷</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">鐵氧體粉塵</span>製作離子電池。按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> 在空的<span class=\"name name-technology\">道具欄欄位</span>中製作。<br>鈷能在地底找到。找出天然洞穴入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>許多洞穴內有危險植物。<br>偶爾能在棄置於星球的<span class=\"name name-technology\">補給儲物箱</span>中找到補給品。"
  },
